    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Rare find alert \u2014 this is the one you've been waiting for! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition, meaning it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained \u2014 the exterior is flawless, the interior is pristine, and the mechanics are in top-notch shape. Whether you're a discerning daily driver or a collector looking for something truly special, this car delivers on every front. Don't miss your chance to own a vehicle that truly has it all!",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A wonderful opportunity for the savvy buyer looking for a solid, dependable vehicle without the premium price tag of mint condition! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and runs great, with only the expected minor wear you'd find on a vehicle that's actually been enjoyed. The exterior presents nicely with just a few small cosmetic blemishes, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically sound and ready for the road, this is a car you can feel confident driving every day!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in fair condition, and we want to be fully transparent about what you're purchasing. The exterior shows visible signs of wear \u2014 expect moderate scratches, some minor dents, and paint that has lost some of its original luster in places. The interior is functional but shows everyday use: upholstery has some wear spots and there may be minor scuffs on trim panels. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance attention in the near future. This is an honest, no-surprises listing \u2014 what you see is what you get. A solid option for a buyer looking for a usable vehicle at a fair price, with the understanding that some cosmetic and minor mechanical attention may be needed down the road.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, best suited for buyers who are comfortable with a significant project or are looking for a parts vehicle. The exterior shows substantial wear, including faded and chipped paint, visible rust in multiple areas, and body panel damage that would require professional repair or replacement. The interior is worn throughout \u2014 torn upholstery, cracked dashboard materials, and non-functional features are present. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require meaningful investment to return to reliable daily-driver status. We are not hiding anything: this is a distressed vehicle sold as-is. If you're a hands-on enthusiast, a mechanic looking for a project, or someone needing parts, this could be a worthwhile purchase at the right price. Please inspect thoroughly before buying.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Practical & Honest \u2013 A Fair-Condition Ride Ready for Daily Use! \ud83d\ude99\n\nNeed a reliable set of wheels without the premium price tag? This could be the one! We'll be completely upfront with you: this vehicle is in fair condition, meaning it runs and drives but shows its age with some visible wear, minor cosmetic imperfections, and the occasional quirk you'd expect from a well-used car. Nothing that should stop you from getting where you need to go! It's a solid everyday driver for someone who wants transportation without overpaying. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs \u2014 priced honestly to reflect exactly what you're getting!",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a complete and honest picture before you make any decisions. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface blemishes and light wear consistent with normal use. You'll notice a small scuff or two on the bumpers and perhaps a faint scratch here and there, but nothing that detracts significantly from the car's overall appearance. The body panels are straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept \u2014 the upholstery shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and high-touch surfaces, but there are no tears, stains, or odors of concern. All interior controls, infotainment, and comfort features are fully functional. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs reliably. The engine starts cleanly, idles smoothly, and delivers confident performance on the road. Brakes, steering, and suspension feel solid with no unusual noises or handling concerns. This is a dependable, everyday driver that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
